Date: Tue, 22 Aug 2006 20:49:36
From: Jila Ghomeshi < ghomeshi@cc.umanitoba.ca >
Subject: Workshop on Determiners 
 

Full Title: Workshop on Determiners 

Date: 25-Nov-2006 - 25-Nov-2006
Location: Winnipeg, Manitoba, Canada 
Contact Person: Jila Ghomeshi
Meeting Email: ghomeshi@cc.umanitoba.ca
Web Site: http://www.umanitoba.ca/linguistics/ghomeshi/determiners.htm 

Linguistic Field(s): Semantics; Syntax 

Call Deadline: 15-Sep-2006 

Meeting Description:

A one-day workshop on the syntax and semantics of determiners sponsored by the
University of Manitoba, will be held in Winnipeg, Manitoba on Saturday November
25, 2006. Abstracts are invited for papers to fill five 20-minute slots.

Please send a short abstract (one page maximum) as a pdf or word attachment to
Jila Ghomeshi at ghomeshi@cc.umanitoba.ca.

In the body of the message please include the following information:

Name of author(s) 
Title of paper 
Institutional affiliation 
e-mail address 

Call deadline: September 15, 2006
Notification of acceptance: October 1, 2006

Confirmed Participants:
Diane Massam, University of Toronto 
Eric Mathieu, University of Ottawa 
Ileana Paul, University of Western Ontario 
Martina Wiltschko, University of British Columbia 

Please feel free to direct any enquiries to the workshop organizer, Jila
Ghomeshi, at ghomeshi@cc.umanitoba.ca.



	
